TITLE:
	This is the README for assignment #7 for astro 598 monte carlo methods

SYNOPSIS:
	In the provided folder is the python file to generate the plots of interest, as well as print the slope. 

	In order to run this on Hyak, first obtain an interactive session qsub -I -V. 
	Load anaconda via 
	>> module load anaconda_2.3

	Then, run the program and visualize the plots and slope as follows:
	>> python hw7.py 

	The slope found is approximately 0.83 for part c. 
	
